<p><strong>Skills</strong> Perception +3</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 1 (200 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Rampage.</em></strong> When the hyena reduces a creature to 0 hit points with a melee attack on its turn, the hyena can take a bonus action to move up to half its speed and make a bite attack.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Bite.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 10 (2d6 + 3) piercing damage.</p>

